Leslie O'Neal played right defensive end. 
</P>
<P>
	Cunningham said right end Dan Williams, back with the Chiefs  
after holding out all last season, will likely miss the exhibition 
opener Sunday with a quadriceps injury. 
</P>
<P>
	Williams is 95 percent recovered, but now is suffering from a  
bad cold, brought on in part by staying inside with the injury on 
ice. 
  	   	
