said. The right-hander received a cortisone shot in April and has 
spent two stints on the DL this year while coming back from 
shoulder surgery that forced him to miss the 1998 season. 
</P>
<P>
	Fernandez allowed four earned runs Wednesday and wasn't involved  
in the decision. He's 6-7 with a 2.98 ERA. 
  	   	
